through the streets.

297
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:03,760
Deal?

298
00:15:04,160 --> 00:15:04,960
A gentleman's word...

299
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:06,040
Is his bond!

300
00:15:08,520 --> 00:15:09,680
On the day of your parade,

301
00:15:10,160 --> 00:15:11,240
I'll open a cask of fine spirit

302
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:12,200
to celebrate.

303
00:15:13,280 --> 00:15:14,680
How do you know

304
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:16,120
it won't be you

305
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:17,720
