307
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:35,400
Flowers!

308
00:15:35,880 --> 00:15:37,440
Clay oven rolls!

309
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:41,040
How much for one of these storybooks?

310
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:42,280
Five cash each.

311
00:15:42,480 --> 00:15:42,920
Oh,

312
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:44,000
