Looks like

323
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:07,920
it's time

324
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:10,200
to open a branch
of Lu's Book Club in the capital.

325
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:12,640
Not bad.

326
00:16:13,680 --> 00:16:14,440
Miss Lu.

327
00:16:29,360 --> 00:16:31,240
The two of you must have invited me over

328
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:34,280
because you have
a lot to say to me, right?

329
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:36,480
Go ahead.

330
00:16:37,280 --> 00:16:38,120
Speak your mind.

331
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,400
Manners unrefined

332
00:16:41,040 --> 00:16:42,120
and speech crude,

333
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:44,920
you are truly unpresentable.

334
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:45,920
Tsk.

335
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:46,800
Yunxi.

336
00:16:50,400 --> 00:16:51,520
