337
00:16:51,760 --> 00:16:54,000
you certainly live up to your reputation

338
00:16:54,520 --> 00:16:55,880
for grace and poise.

339
00:16:56,560 --> 00:16:57,760
You flatter me, Miss Lu.

340
00:16:58,440 --> 00:17:00,000
Though I'm the daughter
of the grand chancellor

341
00:17:00,520 --> 00:17:03,160
and the future mistress
of the Mansion of Prince of Anding,

342
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:05,160
I've always been

343
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:07,120
kind to commoners like you.

344
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:08,720
There's no need to feel nervous.

345
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:10,400
Nervous?

346
00:17:11,640 --> 00:17:12,720
Why would I feel nervous?

347
00:17:13,280 --> 00:17:14,920
Because I'm here to evaluate you,

348
00:17:16,360 --> 00:17:18,120
to see if you're worthy
of his affection.

349
00:17:20,760 --> 00:17:21,720
And if I am?

350
00:17:22,240 --> 00:17:23,880
Will you let us be together?

351
00:17:24,320 --> 00:17:24,960
Naturally.

352
00:17:26,840 --> 00:17:28,720
I'm impressed

353
00:17:29,080 --> 00:17:31,720
by your generosity, Miss Wen.

354
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:33,960
