355
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:35,800
How about

356
00:17:36,840 --> 00:17:38,480
you become my personal maid?

357
00:17:39,360 --> 00:17:41,040
After I marry him,

358
00:17:41,280 --> 00:17:43,920
I'll allow you to be his chief maid.

359
00:17:44,200 --> 00:17:45,240
If his feelings

360
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:47,280
for you persist,

361
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:48,440
I'll make you

362
00:17:48,840 --> 00:17:50,280
his official concubine.

363
00:17:54,080 --> 00:17:55,160
You are so thoughtful.

364
00:17:55,680 --> 00:17:56,320
It's nothing.

365
00:17:57,720 --> 00:17:59,320
Men love to have fun.

366
00:17:59,960 --> 00:18:01,480
Every nobleman

367
00:18:01,560 --> 00:18:04,640
has a few chief maids,

368
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:06,280
concubines,

369
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:08,920
and even mistresses.

370
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:11,840
I've heard of some official wives

371
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:12,840
who, out of jealousy,

372
00:18:13,280 --> 00:18:16,280
throw fits and cause a scene.

373
00:18:16,600 --> 00:18:18,000
A married woman should obey her husband.

374
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,760
Such behavior is just unbecoming.

375
00:18:20,360 --> 00:18:21,240
The official wife

376
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:23,880
should have the dignity and grace

377
00:18:24,520 --> 00:18:25,320
fitting her status.

378
00:18:25,640 --> 00:18:26,120
Stop.

379
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:31,720
What are you doing?

380
00:18:32,800 --> 00:18:34,120
Interesting...

381
00:18:34,800 --> 00:18:36,000
Very interesting.

382
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:37,800
Miss Wen,

383
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:40,200
I've never heard

384
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:42,280
such shameless remarks.

385
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:44,720
I must write them down

386
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:46,320
for my storybooks.

387
00:18:47,320 --> 00:18:48,120
What...?

388
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:50,240
What did you say?

389
00:18:52,520 --> 00:18:53,320
I said

390
00:18:54,040 --> 00:18:55,040
you were shameless.

391
00:18:56,200 --> 00:18:58,080
You call women crazy for love

392
00:18:58,480 --> 00:18:59,520
fools.

393
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:01,220
Yet you show

394
00:19:01,220 --> 00:19:03,520
understanding and forgiveness to those

395
00:19:03,700 --> 00:19:04,880
who break their vows.

396
00:19:06,600 --> 00:19:07,560
In my opinion,

397
00:19:08,040 --> 00:19:10,080
instead of being the daughter
of the grand chancellor,

398
00:19:10,480 --> 00:19:11,400
you should

399
00:19:11,760 --> 00:19:13,900
go and run a cathouse.

400
00:19:14,360 --> 00:19:15,640
I'll rip your mouth off!

401
00:19:16,080 --> 00:19:16,760
Yunxi,

402
00:19:17,520 --> 00:19:18,320
don't be rude.

403
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:26,960
What is a cathouse?

404
00:19:36,440 --> 00:19:37,360
Oh dear,

405
00:19:38,400 --> 00:19:40,520
you are truly sheltered

406
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:43,320
and ignorant of the world outside.

407
00:19:45,720 --> 00:19:46,600
Miss Lu,

408
00:19:47,520 --> 00:19:49,640
