to be my head maid.

409
00:19:50,120 --> 00:19:50,920
You tend to make

410
00:19:52,360 --> 00:19:53,120
inappropriate remarks.

411
00:19:54,480 --> 00:19:55,200
Gosh!

412
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:56,080
Miss Wen,

413
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:57,920
