416
00:20:02,280 --> 00:20:04,000
If you truly want to be with him,

417
00:20:04,840 --> 00:20:07,240
I have a duty
to teach you proper etiquette.

418
00:20:07,560 --> 00:20:08,920
You don't need to feel anxious

419
00:20:09,320 --> 00:20:10,520
or uneasy.

420
00:20:11,320 --> 00:20:13,880
Just stop feeling inferior

421
00:20:14,280 --> 00:20:15,600
