432
00:20:36,080 --> 00:20:37,400
The so-called "feelings"

433
00:20:39,360 --> 00:20:40,240
mean nothing.

434
00:20:40,840 --> 00:20:41,440
Right.

435
00:20:46,040 --> 00:20:46,800
